        <item>
            <id>https://www.ithome.com/0/739/799.htm</id>
            <title>利民推出 30 元的 COGAGE SSD H1 M.2 固态单塔散热器，支持 PCIe 5.0 规范</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/739/799.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/739/799.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 08:07:32 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1790356" rel="nofollow">很宅很怕生</a> 的线索投递！</div>
